efault.aspx website], operated by the County in 1,276-acre Independence Oaks Park |- | Wittenbach/Wege Environmental Center || [[Lowell, Michigan|Lowell]] || [[Kent County, Michigan|Kent]] ||West Michigan || [http://www.lowellschools.com/education/school/school.php?sectionid=1149 website], 140 acres, owned by Lowell School District, outdoor learning center, community garden |- | Woldumar Nature Center || [[Lansing, Michigan|Lansing]] ||[[Eaton County, Michigan|Eaton]] || Central Michigan || [http://www.woldumar.org website], 178 acres, over 5 miles of trails, outreach and on-site Environmental Education programs for children as well as adults |- |}
